      "text": "Confirmed by positive IgM serology and positive RNA PCR. Classic presentation with Koplik spots, cough-coryza-conjunctivitis prodrome, and cephalocaudal maculopapular rash. Exposure likely during travel to Manila, Philippines (March 7-15, 2026). Patient had incomplete MMR vaccination (single dose at 12 months). State case ID: WI-MEAS-2026-0047."
